QuestData.Title: Super Seeds
QuestData.Description: These seeds have been shielded with care by the botani.$b$bGreat power can be felt surging out of these tiny vessels of life.$b$bThese may prove useful.
QuestData.RewardText: I may not know much about farmin' but I do know a power source when I see it. These seeds are packin' quite a punch.$b$bWay to think on yer feet and grab 'em, Commander.
